headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Criminal Elite
content:
Each Heist Finale has its own Elite Challenge which will net a valuable cash bonus upon completion.

Fleeca – Be fast, don’t damage your ride and don’t lose any team lives.
Prison Break – Protect the target, get him out fast and stay alive.
Humane Labs – Beat the timer and keep all team lives.
Series A Funding – Kill your enemies, score a swift time and lose no team lives.
Pacific Standard – Pull off a quick bank job, avoid any NOOSE involvement and lose no team lives.
